{"4216640": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "AIKO: AI Girlfriend 3D Life Sim", "steam_appid": 4216640, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Community</h1><p>Want to try before you buy? Join our Discord for a free demo<br>and connect with other players!<br><br>Your feedback directly shapes AIKO's development — suggest<br>features, report bugs, and chat with the dev team.<br><br></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不是視覺小說。沒有劇本。真正的AI。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  大多數「AI女友」遊戲都是用預設對話假裝AI的視覺小說。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  愛子是真正的AI——每次對話都由先進AI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  即時生成。沒有兩次遊玩 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  是相同的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216640/extras/65a14c1fd8d2a2208e204bbff757020b.avif?t=1776713183\" width=1560 height=878 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>真正的AI對話</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  自然地交談。她理解上下文，記住你過去的對話，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  並以真實的個性回應。給她做一頓飯——她會反應。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  說些有趣的——她下週還記得。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  說任何話——她會讓你驚喜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216640/extras/886fa50ea883ff56bd036c002f812e86.avif?t=1776713183\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216640/extras_big/886fa50ea883ff56bd036c002f812e86.avif?t=1776713183 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><strong>她記住一切</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  你的名字、你的故事、你們的私密笑話。提起上週的事 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  ——她知道。一個真正了解你的夥伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>45種性格特徵</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  害羞、傲嬌、活潑、任性、忠誠，還有40多種。混合搭配，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  創造獨一無二的性格。她會根據</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  你的選擇表現不同。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216640/extras/74eebdb25bb69a6c8026577ec92b44d1.avif?t=1776713183\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><strong>關係進展</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  陌生人 → 熟人 → 朋友 → 密友 → 戀人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  你的言行決定她對你的感覺。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216640/extras/e17510ee93c5fa25323ae26cfe241530.avif?t=1776713183\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><strong>全面自訂</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  10+套裝、內衣、髮型、瞳色、體型。打造你的專屬愛子。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216640/extras/b31108c890421a93f768f72d549f3c41.avif?t=1776713183\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>一起的日常生活</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  在互動小遊戲中一起烹飪。看她度過日常。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  第一人稱探索她的生活空間。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216640/extras/67aff29f0717aaf67f91028ee0c5eedc.avif?t=1776713183\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216640/extras/874c3c1c21536ae72b2a28864d8ff545.avif?t=1776713183\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>語音功能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  用麥克風說話。聽她用自然語音回應。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  即時對話，感覺栩栩如生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 